      "content": "are you sure though? it feels kinda weird, like a pressure that won't go away and it's not just a ringing sound, it's actually silent in that ear. i'm just worried i might have poked something wrong. do you think the peroxide will actually fix it if it's something more serious? i really don't want to end up in the ER if i can just fix it at home.",
